Precis(a) Reappointment of JOHN RONALD LONGSTAFFE, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as chairman of the board of directors of the Vancouver Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term ending June 30, 1997; and (b) approves the reappointment of the said JOHN RONALD LONGSTAFFE as a part-time director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure effective December 29, 1996 and ending on June 30, 1997.
